These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-1::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  engineer, police-officer
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is not the police-officer##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Food    | police-officer   | engineer  |
| Sport   | soccer | volleyball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-2::.
There 2 different types of food: apple, lemon
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cricket, biathlon
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is not the person eating lemon##6

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1   |     2      |
| Food   | apple | lemon      |
| Pet    | cricket  | biathlon |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-3::.
There 2 different types of food: plum, pumpkin
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, january
1. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person eating plum##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is not the person eating plum##6

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |
| Food    | pumpkin  | plum    |
| Sport   | october | january |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-6-4::.
